description:
Alterations to two of the four buildings permitted on application 04/AP/2348.

1. Alterations to building fronting Abbey Street to provide 18 additional dwellings (within existing volume) thereby providing  3 studio units, 35 one bed, 30 two bed and 8 three bed flats, plus the addition of balconies;

2. Alterations to building fronting Tower Bridge Road including elevation alterations and extended roof plant. 

3.New bicycle store
